reviewText:
From reading the other reviews, it seems a lot of people expected a dramatic story from this...  I chalk this up to one of two reasons:  Either they didn't do their research and find out what this was REALLY was before purchasing it (and therefore I hope they didn't pay too much for it); or they were misled by the "description" on Amazon, that doesn't describe anything similar to what's really on this disc.

Yes, this has no story, plot, semblance of a plot, or even dialogue. It's not even shot on film. So if you're looking for a movie about vampire girls, even a bad one, you're not gonna get that.

What it IS, is a bunch of nude and/or scantily-clad chicks gyrating and undulating about in scary witchy leather fetish-style costumes with a few them wearing vampire fangs and putting the bite on other chicks.  Basically, it's a stripper-show for Halloween.  And if you need a good sexy video to set the mood on the bigscreen at YOUR Halloween party while the stereo is cranking out the spooky tunes, this would fit the bill admirably.

The title and cover are slightly misleading, as this dvd is a loosely-knit string of videos w/ attractive babes in kinky outfits, one or two of which are occult-themed. The ladies are all pro-strippers, as their motions would dictate, and we get to see them undress seductively - it`s just like going to a titty-bar (can I say that here?) without leaving your house, which isn`t a bad thing, necessarily. Some of the outfits and women are quite alluring and, thankfully, none go on for too long. But there isn`t a word spoken during the entire outing, it`s all performed to a music track. It clocks in at under an hour, more or less, and I don`t know if that`s a good thing or not - more may have been tedious, but I DID want more being the gluttonous fool that I am. Your call...
